{
  "stem": "5261.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So we're-- we were sitting before the houses.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We couldn't go on the street.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And so, only to breathe the fresh air.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But it was very boring.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was really, for this time, for young people, extremely hard life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I never heard.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never seen-- you know, immediately after the war, from time to time I tried go-- before my-- before I finded this job by bakery, I went by foot to Aleksandrowo.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It is someplace.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were many Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I have seen them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were, with the [INAUDIBLE], walking on the street.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And [? there ?] was still free the bread.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We could buy free without stamps.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And sometimes I-- I-- I bought the bread for my mother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But it was very short time, and then we couldn't never cross this frontier because Aleksandrowo belonged more to the district of Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You must understand that Torun-- they [? tooked ?] as a part of [?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Reichsdeutschland. ?] Because from Berlin to Gdansk, there were-- they called this like corridor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And many trains, like Mitropa with the German railcars, they crossed Torun.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I remember as a child I-- I went-- I shouted some German-- they gave me-- they throw the windows-- some sweets, some bonbons.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But, you see, maybe I will tell you this time when I was working by this bakery.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was very glad, and I wanted to keep this job as so long I can.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And one time when I was delivering the bread, I crossed the German theatre in Torun.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I have seen their displays.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I liked to show-- to see the displays, how looked the-- the actors.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And once I have seen there was written some-- it was written exactly so-- 'Chorus singers wanted.' First, I thought, maybe the German only.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Maybe Poles.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
